title: Executive Order 7600-Amendment of Tariff of United States Consular Fees
content: By virtue of and pursuant to the authority vested in me by section 1745 of the Revised Statutes (U.S.C., title 22, sec. 127), it is ordered that Item 8 of the Tariff of United States Consular Fees be, and it is hereby, amended to read as follows:
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 7600-Amendment of Tariff of United States Consular Fees Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/368950
